HugAgentOS Community Edition

This distribution bundles third-party open source software. Major direct
dependencies and their licenses:

  Backend : FastAPI (MIT), SQLAlchemy (MIT), Alembic (MIT), AgentScope
            (Apache-2.0), mcp (MIT), httpx (BSD-3), structlog (Apache-2.0)
  Frontend: React (MIT), Ant Design (MIT), Zustand (MIT), Univer presets —
            free tiers only (Apache-2.0), Mermaid (MIT), KaTeX (MIT)
  Optional: mem0ai (Apache-2.0), neo4j Python driver (Apache-2.0) — installed
            only with the `mem0` profile (requirements-mem0.txt)

Commercial-licensed components (e.g. @univerjs/preset-sheets-advanced) and
proprietary cloud SDKs (oss2, opensandbox) are NOT part of this distribution;
they ship only with the commercial edition.
